<br>
Wezloc <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umystiszephyr.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mystis Zephyr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 83<br> <font color=#333333>(10/21/02 12:37:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=774.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Updated suggestions on Magician Pet Heals...</span><hr size=1> WEZLOC,<br>
<br>
Rebalancing the level 44, 52, and level 60 pet heals has nothing to do with that thread. Your thread was regardling the new level 64 pet heal and how it relates to the beast lord pet heal. And even if they do the beast lord pet heals are SO far ahead of the magician pet heals ours STILL would not come close...read my post to compare the ratios the beast lord pet heals: <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub6.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showMessage?topicID=7049.topic">pub6.ezboard.com/fthemagi...7049.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
